            description: "For operators commissioning inspection work — how to verify credentials, what to specify, what to pay, and what to avoid.",
            href: "/rpii/finding-an-inspector",
          },
        ]}
      />
      <RelatedPages
        heading="Related reading"
        pages={[
          {
            title: "BS EN 1176 Explained",
            description: "The UK standard that RPII-certified inspectors work to — what it covers, who must comply, and the three inspection regimes.",
            href: "/bs-en-1176",
          },
          {
            title: "Annual Main Inspection",
            description: "The inspection tier that almost universally requires RPII Annual Inspector certification in UK procurement.",
            href: "/bs-en-1176/annual-inspections",
          },
         {
