            description: "How defects are categorised by severity — low, medium, high, very high — and what response each carries.",
            href: "/bs-en-1176/risk-ratings",
          },
        ]}
      />
      <RelatedPages
        heading="Related reading"
        pages={[
          {
            title: "RPII Explained",
            description: "The UK body that certifies the inspectors who work to BS EN 1176 — what RPII is, the inspector grades, and why certification matters.",
            href: "/rpii",
          },
          {
            title: "Finding an RPII Inspector",
            description: "For operators commissioning inspection work — how to verify credentials and choose the right RPII-certified inspector.",
            href: "/rpii/finding-an-inspector",
          },
        ]}
      />
    </div>
  </article>
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(articleSchema)} />
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(faqSchema)} />
</BaseLayout>
